- To build 16x9 pdf file:

$ make

- To build and view (see NOTE)

$ make view

- To clean up

$ make clean

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

NOTE:
 - This is a work in progress.  
 - The idea is to make a .sty file suitable for GA theory slides.
 - To define a viewer, in your shell setup define  
    VIEWER=evince 
    or VIEWER="open -a Preview"
    or VIEWER=xpf

